<dl id="jn1012l"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="jn1" href="#jn1012">JN1: </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/jn1all.htm#jn1012l"> (NLI.2A) 12(l)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font color="green">[The object of desire is that which appears to us <u>beautiful</u> . . . . We / desire a thing because it appears to us <u>good</u> . . . . . . (?) / Met. XII cap. 7]</font></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><mark>L&apos;objet d&eacute;sir&eacute; est ce que nous para&icirc;t &ecirc;tre bien</mark>; et le primitif de la volont&eacute;, c&apos;est le bien m&ecirc;me. <mark>Nous le souhaitons, parce qu&apos;il nous para&icirc;t souhaitable</mark>, bien plut&ocirc;t qu&apos;il ne nous para&icirc;t souhaitable parce que nous le souhaitons. <br>Page Head: <mark>M&Eacute;TAPHYSIQUE</mark> d&apos;ARISTOTE &nbsp; <mark>LIVRE XII, CHAP. VII</mark>, &sect;2 <small> Aristotle, <a name="MABS" href="/udra/udex.htm#MABS"><cite title="source">M&eacute;taphysique d'Aristote</cite></a> (1879), 181f</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: See also <a name="jn1022b" href="jn1all.htm#jn1022b">JN1 (NLI.2A):022(b)</a> below. </mm> </dd></dl>
